		Known Bugs and Limitations

See also: ../bugs

Forth system:
	A constant with value a020 (or a variable at address a020)
causes disaster when compiled and executed.
 
	.s and depth can fail when stacks are small (e.g. 32 cells).
This is because parameter stack is copied to return stack to find depth.

	int: doesn't align dictionary pointer before compiling.

